msgstr "I-akhawunti yakho ihanjiswe apha ukusuka ku-{source}. Kude ukuze uyicime apho, iimessage nezaziso zingafika kumaseva omabini, inxalenye yemixholo yakho iqhubeka isebenziswa kwiseva endala, kwaye abalandeli bangathatha imizuzu embalwa ukukufumana apha."
